How We've Helped Others

Increased Email Reliability with Hosted Exchange – ERA Dawson Bradford Co.

The Problem

Email is critical to our business, and our clients want to be able to communicate with our Realtors 24/7.  Our previous email system was based on older technology requiring us to wait for emails to send and receive and we had frequent service outages.

The Solution

SJ Rollins Technologies solved our problem with a Hosted Exchange solution that increased email reliability, added security, and made sending and receiving mail almost instantaneous. It’s been a great business solution for our brokers and clients.
